Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mighty Little Defenders 2: The Intriguing Alien Guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.77,Title,,0,0,0,,Meeting a New Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:36.98,end,,0,0,0,,End
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Paddi,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to bring all of those nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I were to get lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d just meet you guys at the big tree on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going up there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a meteor shower tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re going up there to watch the shooting stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But “Shooting stars” are just rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve already seen those before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A meteor shower won’t be the only thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a new friend waiting for you up there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for goodness’ sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re always giving us trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.40,0:01:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Brother Weslie and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy! Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to bring so many, but you just wouldn’t listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s BB Goat ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1070)}—Have you seen BB Goat ?　—Have you seen Wilie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilie’s missing, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolnie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,why must we bring so many things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,just to watch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a meteor shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountaintop is totally empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy, Daddy, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,meet my new friend right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven’t seen him this happy in quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down, Wilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s Wilie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We turned around to search, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but we didn’t find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat ’s missing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go search together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy, Daddy, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Wilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is BB Goat .
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going with my parents up the mountain to watch the meteor shower,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends got lost, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You’re {\i0}the one who got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry. Even if I were to get lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d just meet you guys at the big tree on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go find them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad says that when I get lost, I should stay in one spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s dangerous to run around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s just stay put, okay, BB Goat ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be monsters around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,These are dandelions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just blow on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and they’ll fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, BB Goat !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I overheard Wolffy saying
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that he has plans to watch the meteor shower with Weslie and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s so interesting about some random cosmic rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn’t be going
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if it weren’t for the sake of capturing BB Goat .
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is huge, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s BB Goat !
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} BB Goat !
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, Weslie and the others aren’t here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me that they’re lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform into a cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re just two little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We don’t need to do {\i1}that {\i0}much, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If we make too much noise, we risk luring other people over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Brother Wilie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m making a sign for my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If they see it, they’ll be able to follow it and find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,this is me, and this is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If I’m the first to capture that little goat,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can demote His Majesty and become the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you smiling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Goldy can’t do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll take matters into my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll teach you how to pick them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the bait, my fishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I hit something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you hit a beehive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s that goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can’t take this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to capture you right this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mud monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilie made this sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat  must have drawn this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If only my dad were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad says they make wishes come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish my dad would fly over here to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re too young to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he’ll fly over here to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad is amazing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He can also fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad invents things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad captures bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad makes traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad can do everything that your dad can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use the traps that my dad taught me to face the monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are “traps”?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I’ll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m getting you for good this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone’s that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,These are Wilie’s traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we get across?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat ,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,my wish came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad really did fly over here to rescue us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to possess someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1070)}Not the bees again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,870)}Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, BB Goat ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t run off anymore, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Wilie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t run off anymore, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wilie,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,she’s the new friend I was telling you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, BB Goat ’s actually the goat who’s looking for her brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s your new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Brother Wilie was actually my new friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1070)}Yay! I have a new friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.01,0:12:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat ,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,make a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It really will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I find my brother soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope BB Goat  finds her brother soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My wish will come true very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My wish will come true sooner than yours will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine will!
